Diamond Mind (Counter)
Level: Swordsage 5, Warblade 5
Initiation Action: 1 immediate action
Range: Personal
Target: You

This maneuver allows you to make a free attack against a reckless enemy. When a foe provokes an attack of opportunity from you, you initiate this maneuver. As part of this maneuver, you make an immediate melee attack against the foe that provoked the attack of opportunity. This attack does not replace the normal attack of opportunity you receive.
